snippet.title: Katrina blames herself for what happened to Amber | Nang Ngumiti Ang Langit (With Eng Subs)
snippet.description:
Ruth (Matet de Leon) urges Katrina (Cristine Reyes) to stop blaming herself for Mikmik (Sophia Reola) and Amber's (Krystal Mejes) plight.
(With English Subtitles)
